Alex talks with Ben Fuchs, the host of the nationally syndicated radio program on GCN, The Bright Side. Fuchs is a registered pharmacist, nutritionist, cosmetic chemist and founder of EconoComp Pharmacy and Rocky Mountain Natural Laboratories. 

Alex also talks about Obama's State of the Union address, military exercises underway in Los Angeles, and the rolling Ron Paul revolution as the establishment pushes the chicken hawk warmonger Newt Gingrich for the GOP presidential nomination.
